    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，国航将就增持国泰股份征求顾问意见</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/air-china-said-to-consider-raising-stake-in-cathay-pacific</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，近几个月来，中国国航一直在就增持国泰航空近 30% 股份的可能好处征求顾问的意见，这让这位 77 岁的老人重新燃起了长期以来的想法。香港航空公司从疫情中反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/air-china-said-to-consider-raising-stake-in-cathay-pacific</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 08:32:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
